-- KKR, Wendel Complete Sale of Legrand Stake at Price of 23.95 Euros a Share
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-21T08:26:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/kkr-wendel-complete-sale-of-legrand-stake-at-price-of-23-95-euros-a-share.html
Kohlberg Kravis Roberts & Co. and
Wendel completed the sale of a 9 percent stake in Legrand SA at
a price of 23.95 euros a share, the companies said in an emailed
statement.  KKR and Wendel remain the controlling shareholders of
Legrand.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  